#

Gummy Bear Jello Shots

17 min
$10
100 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 12

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Dessert

Tags:

PartyDessertAlcoholicEasy

Description

Fun and fruity jello shots with a gummy bear surprise! Perfect for parties.

Ingredients

  • jello (any flavor): 1 package (3 oz)
  • boiling water: 1 cup
  • cold water: 1/2 cup
  • vodka (or any clear alcohol): 1/2 cup
  • gummy bears: 1 cup
